and Benita knows
exactly what happened.

00:13:32.770 --> 00:13:35.950
So I get there and I gave my
speech and I kind of weave

00:13:35.950 --> 00:13:38.170
in there that we're
still working.

00:13:38.170 --> 00:13:40.850
And at the end of my speech,
Mrs. Barbara Bush comes up

00:13:40.850 --> 00:13:42.240
and she goes, ladies
and gentlemen,

00:13:42.240 --> 00:13:46.180
I have a huge surprise
