00:14:16.780 --> 00:14:22.020
And I'm here today to tell
you [applause]-- so between--

00:14:22.020 --> 00:14:25.250
that was between the years
of 2011 and 2013 and I'm here

00:14:25.250 --> 00:14:28.620
to tell you in 2018,
we still have that.

