00:14:29.920 --> 00:14:31.220
&gt;&gt; Elsa Cardenas-Hagan:
We keep sustainability.

00:14:31.220 --> 00:14:32.520
&gt;&gt; Laura Bailet:
Sustainability, that's huge.

00:14:32.520 --> 00:14:33.980
&gt;&gt; Elsa Cardenas-Hagan: And
so, through this work --

00:14:33.980 --> 00:14:38.530
and I say, you know, Mrs. Bush
